inscription: IN LOVING MEMORY OF CATHERINE COSTELLO LAVEYHOROE. CLOONFAD DIED 27TH DEC. 1948. HER MOTHER MARY MCCORMACK DIED 24TH MARCH 1959. R.I.P. ERECTED BY HER LOVING HUSBAND & FAMILY COSTELLO
IN LOVING MEMORY OF ANNE RUANE LISNAGROOBE DIED MARCH 13-1957. AND HER HUSBAND PATRICK DIED MARCH 8-1972. R. I. P.
JOHN ROA LISNAGROOBE WHO MAY YE AGED 75 RUANE WHO DIEN 179?

SACRED HEART OF JESUS HAVE MERCY ON THE SOUL OF THOMAS RUANE LISNAGROOBE WHO DIED APRIL 16th 1923 AGED 74 YRS AND OF HIS WIFE MARGARET RUANE DIED JULY 26th 1929 AGED 78 YEARS R. I. P. ERECTED BY THEIR FOND SON THOMAS RUANE PHILADELPHIA USA
